{"tid":1868171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［醫護心聲］我諗我有資格講下點解唔罷落去","createTime":"2020-02-07T12:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T17:18:50.000Z","uid":277853,"like":31,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c083911eb20f1a3be29c66da1d939177d7905ee6","tid":1868171,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:11:35.000Z","msg":"有興趣嘅可以睇返我上個Po<br />\n醫護哭訴求圍爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1860199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1860199</a><br />\n多謝各位連登仔嘅鼓勵<br />\n睇到你哋嘅message 我好感動<br />\n<br />\n但係，對於延長罷工，我都投左反對票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實罷工呢幾日，仲攰過返工<br />\n企成日，喺街站又俾人狂鬧<br />\n心理壓力好大，晚晚發惡夢<br />\n驚秋後算賬，更驚爭取唔到得個吉<br />\nOk, 以上真係中哂<br />\n<br />\n有無後悔？無<br />\n點解唔繼續？因為無以為繼<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"> 林奠今次醒</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">拖字訣拖死你</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係，林奠睇穿我哋係一班有良心嘅人，佢知道呢班人唔捨得繼續辛苦其他同事、辛苦病人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對住無賴，無得打喎<br />\n工會有無應對方法？<br />\n抱歉，我睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工會自己嘅strategy<br />\n- 無論係下一步行動如何能迫使政府跪<br />\n- 定係點樣為已被恐嚇或將會被恐嚇嘅同事出頭<br />\n<br />\n都係白卷<br />\n無實質planning只係up話會搵律師團隊傾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">係唔會令同事安心架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我唔係插工會，唔係唔支持工會。我知佢地好辛苦，亦好感激佢地嘅付出。但係，做得唔好嘅真係要拎出黎傾。如果唔係，我地永遠唔會有進步</span><br />\n<br />\n希望工會mon post睇到<br />\n<br />\n再一次多謝各位連登手足<br />\n可以交棒俾你哋嘛？"},{"pid":"e7cf62ccce5b84a86ca601686a4bd11218200806","tid":1868171,"uid":24133,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c083911eb20f1a3be29c66da1d939177d7905ee6","tid":1868171,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:11:35.000Z","msg":"有興趣嘅可以睇返我上個Po<br />\n醫護哭訴求圍爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1860199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1860199</a><br />\n多謝各位連登仔嘅鼓勵<br />\n睇到你哋嘅message 我好感動<br />\n<br />\n但係，對於延長罷工，我都投左反對票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實罷工呢幾日，仲攰過返工<br />\n企成日，喺街站又俾人狂鬧<br />\n心理壓力好大，晚晚發惡夢<br />\n驚秋後算賬，更驚爭取唔到得個吉<br />\nOk, 以上真係中哂<br />\n<br />\n有無後悔？無<br />\n點解唔繼續？因為無以為繼<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"> 林奠今次醒</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">拖字訣拖死你</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係，林奠睇穿我哋係一班有良心嘅人，佢知道呢班人唔捨得繼續辛苦其他同事、辛苦病人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對住無賴，無得打喎<br />\n工會有無應對方法？<br />\n抱歉，我睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工會自己嘅strategy<br />\n- 無論係下一步行動如何能迫使政府跪<br />\n- 定係點樣為已被恐嚇或將會被恐嚇嘅同事出頭<br />\n<br />\n都係白卷<br />\n無實質planning只係up話會搵律師團隊傾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">係唔會令同事安心架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我唔係插工會，唔係唔支持工會。我知佢地好辛苦，亦好感激佢地嘅付出。但係，做得唔好嘅真係要拎出黎傾。如果唔係，我地永遠唔會有進步</span><br />\n<br />\n希望工會mon post睇到<br />\n<br />\n再一次多謝各位連登手足<br />\n可以交棒俾你哋嘛？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:12:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有良心=完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e1fc35cd66fa866bc8184d4eaeaa5101db04471b","tid":1868171,"uid":75364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"09a1db7d881c8cabfd56f2f4fac5770eed90473b","tid":1868171,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"唔捨得繼續辛苦其他同事<br />\n咁咪叫佢地加入罷囉<br />\n<br />\n唔捨得辛苦病人<br />\n咁咪更加要逼林奠全面封關囉等你地可以安心復工囉<br />\n<br />\n連我呢啲廢柴都諗到點駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db30870834a49cc68773c258fee692ab8a5df30e","tid":1868171,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:16:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啲形容係左膠專用<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"8cde89ef5fc9de7ae1426aa2f402f6fbe513b747","tid":1868171,"uid":282855,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:17:42.000Z","msg":"罷工冇次罷得成，會唔會繼續去搶米搶廁紙重大成效呢？"},{"pid":"520fbb781e1fa5f1e5491e022d059452a7071bbb","tid":1868171,"uid":70817,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:18:08.000Z","msg":"樓上d留言真係典型連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地醫護罷左工啦, 你地仲做緊咩？<br />\n搵佢地做代理人幫你地爭取封關?<br />\n自己有冇幫手打輿論戰分擔醫護壓力?<br />\n有冇搞工會準備接力罷工?<br />\n除左用把口叫人點點點,<br />\n有冇諗過自己可以做乜?<br />\n<br />\n多謝醫護, 之後交俾其他人"},{"pid":"042aaf16e60de7030dddb1620d0e8ec4051b6f3c","tid":1868171,"uid":316638,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:18:51.000Z","msg":"無論你哋決定係點，我哋香港人都欠罷工醫護一句：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">多謝你哋！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5876b17b117e4bd6ed77973e349b29ffba1df3b4","tid":1868171,"uid":123764,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"多謝你們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2344c02535dd23fa3930cf77b0831bc5046ac5c9","tid":1868171,"uid":47905,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:20:20.000Z","msg":"咁如果要你無全套裝備照顧有病支那人你會點做<br />\n咁如果乜野高危既事 都搵你或罷過工既同事做 你會點做<br />\n<br />\n明白你覺得無以為繼<br />\n<br />\n但如果面對以上既事你會硬食定係點?<br />\n想知你地返去既心態係放棄反抗 甘心做奴隸<br />\n定係等機會再反擊?"},{"pid":"25794276bc4e23d6b6ed5e9185e14382ac3518c1","tid":1868171,"uid":121750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"星星之火"},{"pid":"f3442c43493523876247b531a8f99c369b0213ab","tid":1868171,"uid":232817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔返住工屌醫護唔繼續罷工，好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f467d1da5fc75a777e751c006e4a159d23845a92","tid":1868171,"uid":232817,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:24:11.000Z","msg":"好聽啲就係恨鐵不成鋼，<br />\n但其實就係想人地付出，然後自己乜都唔洗做，<br />\n明明封關依件係影響全香港人，但就屌醫護唔罷工會害死自己，<br />\n依家隨時衝關嘅人就住你隔離，你乜都唔做都害緊你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3a8e314ff96b22144b211d14e0685bac1611fb7","tid":1868171,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:25:02.000Z","msg":"好多謝真係有罷工嘅每一位<br />\n希望真係星星之火<br />\n<br />\n有人追究想炒一定要報media搞大佢 <br />\n最後 希望你地可以安全渡過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b7c84ba5a34852e1e8a3d092233233a463ae34","tid":1868171,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7cf62ccce5b84a86ca601686a4bd11218200806","tid":1868171,"uid":24133,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c083911eb20f1a3be29c66da1d939177d7905ee6","tid":1868171,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:11:35.000Z","msg":"有興趣嘅可以睇返我上個Po<br />\n醫護哭訴求圍爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1860199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1860199</a><br />\n多謝各位連登仔嘅鼓勵<br />\n睇到你哋嘅message 我好感動<br />\n<br />\n但係，對於延長罷工，我都投左反對票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實罷工呢幾日，仲攰過返工<br />\n企成日，喺街站又俾人狂鬧<br />\n心理壓力好大，晚晚發惡夢<br />\n驚秋後算賬，更驚爭取唔到得個吉<br />\nOk, 以上真係中哂<br />\n<br />\n有無後悔？無<br />\n點解唔繼續？因為無以為繼<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"> 林奠今次醒</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">拖字訣拖死你</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係，林奠睇穿我哋係一班有良心嘅人，佢知道呢班人唔捨得繼續辛苦其他同事、辛苦病人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對住無賴，無得打喎<br />\n工會有無應對方法？<br />\n抱歉，我睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工會自己嘅strategy<br />\n- 無論係下一步行動如何能迫使政府跪<br />\n- 定係點樣為已被恐嚇或將會被恐嚇嘅同事出頭<br />\n<br />\n都係白卷<br />\n無實質planning只係up話會搵律師團隊傾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">係唔會令同事安心架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我唔係插工會，唔係唔支持工會。我知佢地好辛苦，亦好感激佢地嘅付出。但係，做得唔好嘅真係要拎出黎傾。如果唔係，我地永遠唔會有進步</span><br />\n<br />\n希望工會mon post睇到<br />\n<br />\n再一次多謝各位連登手足<br />\n可以交棒俾你哋嘛？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:12:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有良心=完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:25:33.000Z","msg":"係，同batman大戰joker一樣，次次講良心，吃虧只會係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d502291b7538392e5719bec747078587857817","tid":1868171,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下次加油加大力度"},{"pid":"5c63a129bedc072627c632269d2e266511f4199b","tid":1868171,"uid":40999,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:26:04.000Z","msg":"林鄭唔係今次醒，佢次次都用拖字決。對上一次反送中都係用呢招，如果唔係721、831，輸咗啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次輸得咁甘除咗因為你所講嘅問題之外，最大問題係其他工會無跟隨醫護步伐，一齊嚟個誇行業大罷工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感謝醫護勇敢出嚟參與罷工，我哋發咗一場好好嘅夢。但係呢一場夢要醒喇，然後我哋將會迎接大清算。無人會可憐我哋，所謂香港人，反抗。從來都係口號嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6a4e6ebd1b0a33adb796b954f71d1449b9c396","tid":1868171,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7cf62ccce5b84a86ca601686a4bd11218200806","tid":1868171,"uid":24133,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c083911eb20f1a3be29c66da1d939177d7905ee6","tid":1868171,"uid":277853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:11:35.000Z","msg":"有興趣嘅可以睇返我上個Po<br />\n醫護哭訴求圍爐<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1860199\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1860199</a><br />\n多謝各位連登仔嘅鼓勵<br />\n睇到你哋嘅message 我好感動<br />\n<br />\n但係，對於延長罷工，我都投左反對票<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實罷工呢幾日，仲攰過返工<br />\n企成日，喺街站又俾人狂鬧<br />\n心理壓力好大，晚晚發惡夢<br />\n驚秋後算賬，更驚爭取唔到得個吉<br />\nOk, 以上真係中哂<br />\n<br />\n有無後悔？無<br />\n點解唔繼續？因為無以為繼<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"> 林奠今次醒</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">拖字訣拖死你</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係，林奠睇穿我哋係一班有良心嘅人，佢知道呢班人唔捨得繼續辛苦其他同事、辛苦病人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對住無賴，無得打喎<br />\n工會有無應對方法？<br />\n抱歉，我睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n工會自己嘅strategy<br />\n- 無論係下一步行動如何能迫使政府跪<br />\n- 定係點樣為已被恐嚇或將會被恐嚇嘅同事出頭<br />\n<br />\n都係白卷<br />\n無實質planning只係up話會搵律師團隊傾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">係唔會令同事安心架</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我唔係插工會，唔係唔支持工會。我知佢地好辛苦，亦好感激佢地嘅付出。但係，做得唔好嘅真係要拎出黎傾。如果唔係，我地永遠唔會有進步</span><br />\n<br />\n希望工會mon post睇到<br />\n<br />\n再一次多謝各位連登手足<br />\n可以交棒俾你哋嘛？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:12:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有良心=完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:26:16.000Z","msg":"笑左 thx"},{"pid":"8eecd225be3200d31bf7293947c48f811fb2f6ab","tid":1868171,"uid":137616,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:27:03.000Z","msg":"的確 換著係我 見到個公會完全承諾唔到啲咩 我都會擔心自己前途<br />\n但係講真 諗一諗當初點解會罷工 對比下而加得到既成效<br />\n有人會接受半封關 有人承擔唔到冇左份工(雖然復工唔等於冇後果) 亦有人選擇為香港人堅持落去<br />\n無論你地點揀 我都會多謝醫護 比起大部份點都唔捨得罷工既人 你地行左唔易行既第一步<br />\n但而加你地再返工 愈黎愈嚴重 咩保障都冇 真係甘心為人禍賣命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a828caa92004edb9010f487d3ea5bd1baa0996","tid":1868171,"uid":57647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:27:25.000Z","msg":"感謝醫護人員一直作出既付出同努力"},{"pid":"0152ab4443d8b4e0ad255dca970f284d6fd7ae78","tid":1868171,"uid":228645,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"520fbb781e1fa5f1e5491e022d059452a7071bbb","tid":1868171,"uid":70817,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:18:08.000Z","msg":"樓上d留言真係典型連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地醫護罷左工啦, 你地仲做緊咩？<br />\n搵佢地做代理人幫你地爭取封關?<br />\n自己有冇幫手打輿論戰分擔醫護壓力?<br />\n有冇搞工會準備接力罷工?<br />\n除左用把口叫人點點點,<br />\n有冇諗過自己可以做乜?<br />\n<br />\n多謝醫護, 之後交俾其他人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:27:37.000Z","msg":"同連登仔怪前線啲火魔掉唔中狗一9樣<br />\n<br />\n自己咩都唔做,但就怪啲付出晒前途安危嘅人做得唔夠好"},{"pid":"a6ffe0d39d44941e35ffadce13033ad6cd3e536c","tid":1868171,"uid":121750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"25794276bc4e23d6b6ed5e9185e14382ac3518c1","tid":1868171,"uid":121750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"星星之火"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:29:16.000Z","msg":"燒唔燒到落去呢一刻無人知，誠心多謝勇敢既第一把火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20486e9ecb9814b4710edbbe83b129bda5711b7d","tid":1868171,"uid":83865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:32:04.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時上面叫你做乜<br />\n記得跟足black &amp; white <br />\n<br />\neg 入dirty room 嘅gear"},{"pid":"571c62408a2d70a3a65c5579bf817786883d4dac","tid":1868171,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20486e9ecb9814b4710edbbe83b129bda5711b7d","tid":1868171,"uid":83865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:32:04.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到時上面叫你做乜<br />\n記得跟足black &amp; white <br />\n<br />\neg 入dirty room 嘅gear"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"你都on99 你係幾時產生咗復工醫護係有say嘅錯覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/l